{"tid":1306838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】內地寶礦力急割席： 與香港分公司完全獨立經營","createTime":"2019-07-11T10:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T10:10:28.000Z","uid":224195,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16276813e18bf8a3c93f6808ffdc244d70c9db43","tid":1306838,"uid":224195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXYFkgM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXYFkgM.png&h=03216338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本能量飲品寶礦力水特決定抽起在無綫（TVB）賣廣告，昨日就因應事件帶來的不便致以誠懇道歉。官媒央視新聞發文批評，寶礦力香港分公司的道歉絲毫看不出道歉。中國內地寶礦力水特公司今日發出聲明「割席」，指內地寶礦力水特與香港寶礦力水特是兩個完全獨立的經營主體，對香港出現的狀況深感遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190711&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59812720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190711%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59812720&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852y8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=5886b751\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190711%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59812720&h=8f65ff0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190711&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59812720</a>"},{"pid":"4a4716f836e909051ffaeffe317b59cbb94ba3a1","tid":1306838,"uid":225347,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"記住，寶抗力唔落tvb廣告只係商業決定，而我飲佢只係因為佢好飲，所以冇咩關係"},{"pid":"94ca628d2856299063d81bb9604fb535a53c6dca","tid":1306838,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4716f836e909051ffaeffe317b59cbb94ba3a1","tid":1306838,"uid":225347,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"記住，寶抗力唔落tvb廣告只係商業決定，而我飲佢只係因為佢好飲，所以冇咩關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}